snippet.title: All Lego Sets Ever Made - Colors and Large Sets
snippet.description:
I hope you enjoyed seeing all lego sets ever made! Let me know if you enjoyed the visualizations!

Data: https://www.kaggle.com/rtatman/lego-database/data
Lego Color Timeline: https://i.stack.imgur.com/AqJCD.jpg
Music: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k9m1Che05-s

Such a throwback. I played with legos all the time, which set was you favorite?

if you want more data story videos like this, leave a like and subscribe!
